metadata.name: Holey People Migrated Token #1
metadata.description: This token has been migrated to a new contract, and you have been airdropped an the original token you owned on the new contract. Same artwork, just on a new contract which will enable us to move this project forward. The Opensea url for the new contract is https://opensea.io/collection/holey-people. The Etherscan url is https://etherscan.io/address/0x2db0be2d34d6de21327d8e3f5ae76a524464bfa7. If you do not see the new token in your main listing of NFTs, please check your hidden items folder. Please check our discord or twitter for more info and contact us with any questions
